{"tid":1006659,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"【幾乎漏了他】產婦誕女後縫針體內還有一個頭！懵然不知懷孖胎","createTime":"2019-02-03T07:04:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-03T10:51:44.000Z","uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"8908e4ecfd8de4c87a16091d41b00936fab1f961","tid":1006659,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-03T07:04:10.000Z","msg":"美國密歇根州一名新手媽媽一直不知道自己懷上雙胞胎，直至誕下女兒後準備縫合傷口時，才驚悉自己還有一個兒子。她相隔59分鐘後誕子，坦言既高興又震驚。<br />\n31歲的妮可（Nicole）完全不知一直懷上孖胎，因為她與34歲丈夫齊默（Matthew Ziesemer）本決定在家中自然分娩，因此懷孕時未曾接受產前掃描。她在去年12月底，懷孕36周時穿了羊水，只好趕到醫院待產，由於作動了逾45小時，最後選擇無痛分娩，並在12月30日誕下女兒布萊克莉（Blakeley）。<br />\n妮可誕女後仍感十分痛楚，完全不合常理，一度令醫生憂心。當護士想為她縫合陰道傷口時，發現「還有些東西在裡面」，於是進行緊急超聲波檢查，驚見妮可體內還有一胎，她之後再誕下兒子凱德（Cade）。<br />\n妮可入院時才做了第一次產前檢查，但當時醫生也未察覺她懷上雙胞胎，估計凱德是被姐姐布萊克莉完全遮擋了。妮可坦言生下雙胞胎又高興又震驚，當護士告知她懷雙胞胎時還以為對方說謊，「我懷雙胞胎一直毫無徵兆，事實上大家都說我的肚子很小，因此我們一直以為唯一的驚喜便是胎兒的性別。」<br />\n由於凱德出生後呼吸有問題，要立即搶救，妮可現時只希望一對子女健康成長。家人又告訴妮可她祖母的表親都曾誕下雙胞胎及三胞胎，因此她誕下孖胎可說是家族傳統。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190202/large/1549093425_070a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190202%2Flarge%2F1549093425_070a.jpg&h=d509e3c1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190202/large/1549094157_1490.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190202%2Flarge%2F1549094157_1490.jpg&h=01709b74&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n凱德（右圖左）比姐姐布萊克莉晚59分鐘出世<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20190203/59215045\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190203%2F59215045&d=6VpbUQS5Cy4QwgKrD6%2Fp7jmKloJy7KF%2B4xCSYNi8ivs%3D&h=45e99fe8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190203%2F59215045&h=0ba84778\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20190203/59215045</a>"},{"pid":"c7fa86bdfa19c855545df070102ac61cc292db32","tid":1006659,"uid":208726,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-03T07:06:39.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ce511b9e06c78e61e5b9180d7b6cff6222cd0fca","tid":1006659,"uid":21249,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-03T07:09:16.000Z","msg":"第一胎打算在家中自然分娩 <br />\n對仔女之後係咪會唔打vaccine同埋vegan飲食 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown4.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"538789076cbe93d0f4d96c06a9931cfdf62f8d45","tid":1006659,"uid":82829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ce511b9e06c78e61e5b9180d7b6cff6222cd0fca","tid":1006659,"uid":21249,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-03T07:09:16.000Z","msg":"第一胎打算在家中自然分娩 <br />\n對仔女之後係咪會唔打vaccine同埋vegan飲食 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown4.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-03T07:33:05.000Z","msg":"反疫苗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"040b40952db997604784e84514388b47a31f83de","tid":1006659,"uid":9286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-03T10:51:44.000Z","msg":"連產前掃描都慳<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/chicken1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/chicken2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/chicken3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}